snippet.title: DUBIUM | Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
🔸Wishlist on Steam: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1234040/DUBIUM/
🔻🔻CLICK HERE🔻🔻

DUBIUM is a Next-level Social Deduction Game with 5-players set in a near-future sci-fi universe. 
A team of 4 frontiers and 1 traitor try to complete missions and escape from a space station while collaborating, betraying, and sneak-attacking each other.

🔸Join our Discord:
https://discord.gg/jPDbXPmPmh


🔸Follow us:
https://twitter.com/Dubiumgame
https://www.facebook.com/Dubiumgame


🔸Official website:
https://www.dubium.com

#DUBIUM #dubiumgame #videogames
